targets.query: SELECT mean("value") FROM "siem_stat" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "appname" = 'enricher' AND "section" = 'query_full_scans') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "subsection" fill(none)
SELECT first("counter") FROM "siem_metric_total" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "group" = 'query_exec' AND "service" = 'router') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "name" fill(none)
